<p>原题链接：<a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/1791/problem/F" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://codeforces.com/contest/1791/problem/F<ExternalLinkIcon/></a><br>
题意：<br>
有n个数组，有m个操作：<br>
1.1 l r：将l~r内的a[i]变成a[i]的位数之和。<br>
2.2 x:询问a[x]的值。</p>
